node.title: Three-vehicle crash leaves one seriously injured in Manukau
node.description: One person has been left seriously injured in a three-vehicle crash in Manukau.
node.content:
["One person has been left seriously injured in a three-vehicle crash in Manukau.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Patrice Allen\n
", "Emergency services are responding to the incident on Reagan Road this evening.", "The road is blocked near the crash site and cordons are in place.", "Motorists have been asked to avoid the area."]
